sanityHomePage.hpIntro: With years of development and UI/UX design under my belt, I can boost the efficiency of your app's user flow.

hpServiceBlockLT.blockText: Reel in visitors with a branded design that speaks your message. Each element is weighed against the global, organic theme for a unified, professional feel.

hpServiceBlockRT.blockText: Guide your visitors to go where you want them to go & do what you want them to. Armed with an understanding of the goals you set for the site, the structure can feature clear, uncluttered indicators and user flows.
